1. *Incident* se dogodio sinoć u gradu. (*Incident* happened last night in the city.) 
2. Ova situacija je opasna, moguće je da dođe do *incidenta*. (This situation is dangerous, it is possible that an *incident* may occur.) 
3. *Incident* se dogodio na autoputu zbog lošeg vremena. (*Incident* occurred on the highway due to bad weather.) 
4. Oni su se *incidentno* sreli u tržnom centru. (They met *incidentally* in the shopping mall.) 
5. Prema *incidentskom* izveštaju, sve je bilo u redu. (According to the *incident* report, everything was fine.) 
6. Njihov *incident* je bio posledica nesporazuma. (Their *incident* was a result of a misunderstanding.) 
7. Naša firma je doživela *incident* sa konkurentskom kompanijom. (Our company had an *incident* with a rival company.) 
8. Policija je brzo intervenisala u *incidentu* i uspela da smiri situaciju. (The police quickly intervened in the *incident* and managed to calm the situation.) 
9. On je napustio posao nakon što se desio *incident*. (He quit his job after the *incident* occurred.) 
10. Sudija je morao da razmatra slučaj *incidenta* na utakmici. (The judge had to consider the case of the *incident* at the match.)